697
00:40:18,041 --> 00:40:20,168
and even called an ambulance
right after the assault.

698
00:40:20,251 --> 00:40:22,587
Therefore, we argue

699
00:40:22,670 --> 00:40:24,589
that the defendant was not incapable

700
00:40:24,672 --> 00:40:26,591
