of the defendant's condition

704
00:40:33,973 --> 00:40:35,516
after taking the prescribed medication

705
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:39,562
to determine whether she was in a state
of mental incapacity during the incident.

706
00:40:40,521 --> 00:40:42,148
What is the prosecution's position?

707
00:40:42,774 --> 00:40:45,068
While I question
the necessity of the evaluation,

708
00:40:45,818 --> 00:40:47,946
I will follow Your Honor's judgment.

709
00:40:48,029 --> 00:40:50,990
All right, we'll commission
the evaluation.

710
00:40:51,616 --> 00:40:54,369
Counsel, prepare and submit
the evaluation request form.

