in a particular state,

764
00:46:24,448 --> 00:46:26,909
knowing what might happen.

765
00:46:26,993 --> 00:46:30,454
For example,
if someone plans to commit murder

766
00:46:30,538 --> 00:46:32,915
and drinks on purpose
to calm their nerves or gain courage,

767
00:46:32,999 --> 00:46:36,877
