just because they were drunk.

768
00:46:36,961 --> 00:46:41,215
Normally, they could claim
diminished capacity due to intoxication,

769
00:46:41,299 --> 00:46:44,719
but since they drank on purpose,
it doesn't count.

770
00:46:45,344 --> 00:46:49,515
