to become like Wonder Woman,

775
00:46:59,025 --> 00:47:01,485
the prosecutor could reject

776
00:47:01,569 --> 00:47:03,446
her mental incapacity plea

777
00:47:03,529 --> 00:47:06,198
as an act of voluntary intoxication.

778
00:47:06,282 --> 00:47:10,202
Does that mean she can't be acquitted
by pleading mental incapacity?

779
00:47:11,787 --> 00:47:12,663
Yes.

